reviewText: This was a night of a lot of funny jokes . you won't be disappointed. Great price thank you very much.
This DVD is really funny. It's soo good to see and hear these comics before their careers took off they are all so funny from the beginning up to now.
arrived on time shows well, no problems and the comedy is good which is a plus for me. So Im happy with it
The DVD is of course part of the old genration videotaping. we are spoiled by HD imaging today and anything else is not that satisfactory.
Very very very funny. All of the DVDs are funny and it is defiantly worth the price. Highly recommend it.

I have this DVD and it's extremely funny. But yet you can never go wrong with Martin Lawrence. I would watch it once and it would be on repeat all day before I realize how many times I've watched it and laughed. You can't go wrong with this one.
